# PDF Highlight Rendering

## Problem

Current PDF highlight rendering works but lacks:
1. Selection mode feedback (text vs region)
2. Confidence-based visual styling
3. Hover states and interaction consistency
4. Orphaned highlight indicators

## Current Implementation

**Annotation Layer** (`pdf-page-element.ts:2954-3005`):
```typescript
setHighlights(highlights: PageHighlight[]): void {
  this.annotationLayerEl.innerHTML = '';
  for (const highlight of highlights) {
    for (const rect of highlight.rects) {
      const el = document.createElement('div');
      el.className = 'pdf-highlight';
      el.dataset.annotationId = highlight.annotationId;
      el.style.cssText = `...`;
      el.addEventListener('click', ...);
      this.annotationLayerEl.appendChild(el);
    }
  }
}
```

**SVG Annotation Layer** (`pdf-annotation-layer.ts`):
- Alternative SVG-based rendering
- Blend mode filter for better appearance

## Solution

### Phase 1: Visual Feedback

1. Add selection mode indicator (text cursor vs crosshair)
2. Add highlight confidence styling (solid vs dashed border)
3. Add orphaned highlight indicator (warning icon)
4. Improve hover states

### Phase 2: Interaction Polish

1. Add highlight preview during selection
2. Add drag-to-adjust highlight bounds
3. Add multi-select for batch operations
4. Keyboard navigation between highlights

### Phase 3: Performance

1. Use canvas-based rendering for high highlight counts
2. Virtualize highlights outside viewport
3. Debounce re-renders during scroll

## Tasks

- [ ] Add selection mode visual indicator
- [ ] Implement confidence-based styling (solid/dashed)
- [ ] Add orphaned highlight warning icon
- [ ] Improve hover states (color preview, actions)
- [ ] Add highlight preview during selection
- [ ] Implement keyboard navigation
- [ ] Add virtualization for many highlights
- [ ] Create highlight interaction tests

## Styling Proposal

```css
/* High confidence - solid */
.pdf-highlight[data-confidence="high"] {
  border: none;
  background: rgba(255, 235, 59, 0.4);
}

/* Medium confidence - subtle dashed */
.pdf-highlight[data-confidence="medium"] {
  border: 1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  background: rgba(255, 235, 59, 0.3);
}

/* Low confidence (visual match only) */
.pdf-highlight[data-confidence="low"] {
  border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.5);
  background: rgba(255, 235, 59, 0.2);
}

/* Orphaned - could not re-anchor */
.pdf-highlight[data-orphaned="true"] {
  border: 2px dashed rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.5);
  background: rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.1);
}
```

## Files to Modify

- `src/reader/renderer/pdf/pdf-page-element.ts` - Enhanced rendering
- `src/reader/renderer/pdf/pdf-annotation-layer.ts` - SVG styling
- `src/reader/renderer/pdf/pdf-selection-handler.ts` - Mode indicator
- `styles.css` - Add highlight confidence styles

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Selection mode visually indicated
- [ ] Confidence reflected in highlight appearance
- [ ] Orphaned highlights clearly marked
- [ ] Smooth hover interactions
- [ ] Keyboard navigation works

## Dependencies

- PDF Highlights Core

