- `src/services/UrlMetadataService.ts`

## Context
Replace ZoomOrchestrator usage with ZoomStateManager in pdf-infinite-canvas.ts.
This is the main wiring task that connects ZoomStateManager to the rendering pipeline.

## File
`apps/amnesia/src/reader/renderer/pdf/pdf-infinite-canvas.ts`

## Changes Required

### 1. Replace ZoomOrchestrator instantiation (~line 445-460)
```typescript
// BEFORE
this.zoomStateMachine = new ZoomOrchestrator({...});

// AFTER
this.zoomStateManager = getZoomStateManager() ?? createZoomStateManager({
  minZoom: this.cameraConstraints.minZoom,
  maxZoom: this.cameraConstraints.maxZoom,
  pixelRatio: window.devicePixelRatio || 2,
  softConstraintFactor: 0.3,
});
```

### 2. Replace onZoomGesture calls (~line 4068-4091)
```typescript
// BEFORE
this.zoomStateMachine.onZoomGesture(zoom, this.getFocalPoint());

// AFTER
this.zoomStateManager.onZoomGesture(zoom, this.getFocalPoint());
```

### 3. Replace epoch/renderVersion usage
```typescript
// BEFORE
++this.renderVersion;

// AFTER
// Epoch auto-increments in ZoomStateManager.onZoomGesture()
const epoch = this.zoomStateManager.getEpoch();
```

### 4. Subscribe to state changes for CSS transforms
```typescript
this.zoomStateManager.subscribe((state) => {
  this.camera = { x: state.position.x, y: state.position.y, z: state.zoom };
  this.applyTransform();
});
```

