|----------|----------------------|-----|
| `mupdf-epub-content-provider.ts:74` | Chapter cache Map, 5min TTL | No tier, no pressure handling |
| `mupdf-epub-content-provider.ts:77` | Resource cache Map, 30min TTL | No tier, no pressure handling |
| `shadow-dom-renderer.ts:146` | Spine content array | Good (L3) |
| `shadow-dom-renderer.ts:149` | Chapter elements Map | Good (L1) |

