## Problem
`constrainCameraPositionPreservingFocalPoint()` has different formulas for "content fits" vs "content exceeds":
```typescript
if (contentScreenWidth > vpWidth) {
  const minX = vpWidth / z - contentWidth;  // One formula
} else {
